A cyberpunk-style digital illustration of a sleek penguin made of glowing circuit boards and neon blue RAM chips, sprinting at incredible speed through a dark futuristic cityscape. Motion blur trails of electric cyan and magenta light stream behind it. The penguin's body appears translucent, revealing intricate motherboard patterns and pulsing data streams flowing through its form. Holographic file folders and document icons scatter in its wake like digital debris. The background features towering server rack buildings with flickering LED lights and streaming binary rain. The atmosphere is electric and dynamic, emphasizing raw computational power and velocity. Dark purple and deep blue color palette with bright neon accents creating dramatic contrast.
